description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at a game centered around one of YouTube's more controversial brands. It's been a while since I've played an indie horror game that was both such a joke and yet decently made. Can I escape the Lunchly factory? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: MrBeast Lunchly Horror Game...
